---
import { QuestionCard } from "@components/ui/Card";
import Paragraph from "@components/ui/Paragraph";
import SmallTitle from "@components/ui/SmallTitle";
---

<div
  class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 mb-16"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-center">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-6">
          <div class="p-3 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <SmallTitle className="mb-0"> Actualités intelligentes </SmallTitle>
        </div>

        <Paragraph className="mb-6">
          Transformez l'actualité en opportunité d'apprentissage. Notre IA
          analyse les derniers événements et crée des flashcards qui renforcent
          votre culture générale.
        </Paragraph>

        <div class="mb-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="w-1/3">
              <div
                class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full inline-flex"
              >
                Par média
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
                Le Figaro, New York Times, The Guardian...
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-1/3">
              <div
                class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full inline-flex"
              >
                Par catégorie
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
                Politique, Économie, Sciences, Culture...
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-1/3">
              <div
                class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full inline-flex"
              >
                Sur mesure
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">
                Créez vos propres collections thématiques
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-500"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Transformez les actualités en flashcards éducatives
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-500"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Apprenez les concepts clés derrière les événements
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-purple-500"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            >
              <path
                fill-rule="evenodd"
                d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Restez informé tout en développant votre culture générale
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div
          class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm"
        >
          <div class="mb-4">
            <div
              class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2 mb-1"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <SmallTitle className="mb-0"> Nouvelle actualité </SmallTitle>
            </div>
            <Paragraph>
              Trump accueille un «sommet» sur les cryptomonnaies à la Maison
              Blanche ce vendredi
            </Paragraph>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 mb-4">
            <div class="font-semibold text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">
              Flashcards générées automatiquement :
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <QuestionCard className="flex flex-col items-start p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 mb-1">
                  Qu'est-ce que la cryptomonnaie ?
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
                  Cliquer pour voir la réponse
                </div>
              </QuestionCard>

              <QuestionCard className="flex flex-col items-start p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 mb-1">
                  Quels sont les enjeux politiques des cryptomonnaies ?
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
                  Cliquer pour voir la réponse
                </div>
              </QuestionCard>

              <QuestionCard className="flex flex-col items-start p-4">
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 mb-1">
                  Évolution de la position de Trump sur les cryptos
                </div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
                  Cliquer pour voir la réponse
                </div>
              </QuestionCard>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex space-x-2">
            <button
              class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-purple-200 transition-colors"
            >
              Sauvegarder
            </button>
            <button
              class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors"
            >
              Enrichir
            </button>
            <button
              class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-emerald-200 transition-colors"
            >
              Partager
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
